## Additional Terms

### Woodworking Calculations Disclaimer

This software provides woodworking calculations based on industry-standard 
formulas and best practices. However:

- The calculations are provided "as-is" without warranty of any kind
- Users must verify all measurements and structural calculations
- Always consult local building codes for structural elements
- Test joinery and techniques on scrap material first
- Use appropriate safety equipment when woodworking
- The author assumes no liability for project outcomes or safety

### Reference Data Attribution

Wood species data compiled from:
- USDA Forest Products Laboratory publications
- Wood Database (www.wood-database.com)
- Industry-standard woodworking references

Joinery and hardware specifications based on:
- Traditional woodworking texts
- Manufacturer specifications (Blum, Accuride, Kreg, etc.)
- Industry best practices and standards

